            "answer_text": "TRILUMINOS Display can show a wider range of colors than most other TVs. ie it\u2019s display provides a color gamut that is 50 percent larger than the ones offered by the conventional LCD display panels. LED light is passed through a film of quantum dots in the TRILUMINOS display to produce the colors this technology uses quantum dots that are none other than light emitting nano-particles (2-10 nano meters). These components emit light at a precise wavelength based on their size, which the human eye can perceive as a particular color. ",
